y operation that accepts a string. We could limit the maximum string size to 256 (as DDS does).\r\n\r\nhttp://stackoverflow.com/questions/27970321/limit-on-dds-topic-names\r\n\r\nWe also have to check the topic lengths when reading from the network. This will involve to modify some of the Unpack() methods in the Packet class.\r\n\r\nP.D: idea and text from @caguero ", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Right now there's no restriction on the maximum length of a topic. There's a potential attack if you use a huge topic name in any operation that accepts a string. We could limit the maximum string size to 256 (as DDS does).</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://stackoverflow.com/questions/27970321/limit-on-dds-topic-names\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">http://stackoverflow.com/questions/27970321/limit-on-dds-topic-names</a></p>\n<p>We also have to check the topic lengths when reading from the network. This will involve to modify some of the Unpack() methods in the Packet class.</p>\n<p>P.D: idea and text from @caguero </p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": {"display_name": "nampi", "uuid": "{89a67bdd-09e6-4c17-8014-48d97fa5c4c8}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B89a67bdd-09e6-4c17-8014-48d97fa5c4c8%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B89a67bdd-09e6-4c17-8014-48d97fa5c4c8%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:6509b6f8-6263-4504-9cee-d12b08b0b4e8/38230840-603b-4875-93fb-c2e81928dd69/128"}}, "nickname": "nampi", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:6509b6f8-6263-4504-9cee-d12b08b0b4e8"}, "state": "resolved", "version": null, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2016-05-26T23:50:48.331048+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2016-08-02T17:57:06.477454+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 43}